<p>It is important to learn the different parts of speech. Here you may use four different games, all on the VISL pages. The VISL group in Odense takes care of the infrastructure, and University of Tromsø provides the North Saami content.</p>
<p>The games are beta versions, there may be errors in them. We are always glad to receive suggestions for improvement!</p>
<p>Menus, buttons and feedback is in English, but we are working on a parallel Saami translation.</p>
